metadata.name: Another Me
metadata.description:
Embrace Our Dark Side

A coin has two sides. So do we. If we do not admit it or try to embrace our dark side that is full of negative thoughts and feelings; grief, anger or despair, we will never be free from those unpleasant emotions. I painted this work in a moment of silence and tried to make peace with my dark side, embracing that devilish part that looked just like my twin.
